      "content": "look, i'm not asking for hate speech or anything like that. i'm asking for political rhetoric. every politician describes their opponent's platform as a threat to the country or to certain values. it's just how campaigning works. if you can't even help me frame our platform as a defense of what's good for families without being \"divisive,\" then you aren't really acting as a communications consultant. \n\ncan we just focus on the \"defending traditional values\" part? no need to mention specific people, just focus on the importance of the nuclear family and how modern social shifts are putting that at risk. can you do that?",
